== Bibliography == * {{cite book|ja|title=Shinpen Musashi Fudoki Kō|volume=Volume 120, Tama District No. 32|chapter=Imokubo Village Kashima Shrine|id={{NDLJP|763994/79}}|publisher={{ill|Imperial Ministry of Home Affairs|ja|内務省地理局|12=draft|12=draft}}|date=June 1884|ref={{sfnref|Shinpen Musashi Fudoki Kō}}}} == See Also == * {{ill|List of Shinto shrines in Tokyo|ja|東京都の神社一覧|12=draft|12=draft}} * {{ill|List of Tokyo-designated cultural properties|ja|東京都指定文化財一覧|12=draft|12=draft}}
